Module  : BBcode Google
Version : 1.1.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This module will turn [google]search words[/google] into a link that
will search for the search words on Google.


Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "bbcode_google" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "BBcode Google".

